DESCRIPTION:A dark\, side-eyed\, comedy\, sci-fi set in a post-scarcity uto
 pia where citizens must maintain strict emotional regulation in order to re
 tain their citizenship. Trapped in a high-tech correctional facility\, Gabr
 iel (J. Stern) and Lyra (M. Michael)\, face the consequences of their “de
 viant outbursts”.Now\, in order to return home\, they must co-operate on 
 challenges designed to break them and prove their relationship is “harmon
 ious”\, or face banishment into the hostile wastelands forever. Dir.: L. 
 Dubarry.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/harmonise-o
 r-die/
